text: Ace, Aces, ACE or ACES may refer to: * Flying ace, a military pilot who has shot down five or more enemy aircraft in air combat * Ace (Doctor Who), a character in the Doctor Who television series * Ace Frehley (born 1951), rock and roll guitarist and former member of the rock band Kiss * Ace, a slang term for asexuality * Ace (card), a card in a pack of playing cards. ==Related pages== * *
title: Ace
